description: Georgina Mazzeo is a Venezuelan fashion model and social influencer with almost 5M followers on Instagram. For her TI, I used a dataset of 40 high quality images, which I trained for 4000 steps with the usual gradual learning rate. For now I've settled on the final step, which seems really accurate and, as far as I can tell, not too overcooked, as it is working very well with a number of different prompts in various models even without modifying the specific weight of the embedding. Hope you enjoy it!
